loc = get_file_path('custom_covars1.csv')
self.ML.Load_Targets(loc=loc, col_name='sex', data_type='b', dataset_type=
    'custom')
self.assertTrue(self.ML.targets.shape == (5, 1))
self.ML.Clear_Targets()
self.assertTrue(len(self.ML.targets) == 0)
self.ML.Load_Targets(loc=loc, col_name='age', data_type='f', dataset_type=
    'custom', filter_outlier_percent=5)
self.assertTrue(self.ML.targets.shape == (4, 1))
self.ML.Clear_Targets()
self.ML.Load_Targets(loc=loc, col_name='sex', data_type='c', dataset_type=
    'custom')
self.assertTrue(self.ML.targets.shape == (6, 1))
